  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multiple normalizing flow architectures (NSF, MAF, RealNVP, NICE, NAF, UNAF, CNF, etc.)",
    "LazyDistribution and LazyTransform for conditional flows",
    "PyTorch nn.Module integration with GPU support",
    "Autoregressive, coupling, and spline-based transformations",
    "Neural and polynomial transformations",
    "Bayesian inference support",
    "Custom flow composition",
    "Variational autoencoder integration"
